Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.81,0:01:30.51,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}她说着低下了头
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.61,0:01:37.41,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}这一夜 我流泪了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.14,0:01:45.00,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}冰冷彻骨 仿如冻雨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.20,0:01:51.96,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}洒落的现实 无处可避
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.54,0:01:58.70,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}生存就是战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.81,0:02:02.43,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}仅为这理由而束缚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.53,0:02:05.32,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}My Heart  My Story
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.48,0:02:12.81,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}泪光对面 看到了光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.02,0:02:19.51,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}小小的窗上 映出旧时晴空
