Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.66,0:00:02.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.75,0:00:04.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利冯兹·阿尔马克
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.77,0:00:08.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘恩负义啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.96,0:00:13.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能获得这种能力 全归功于我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.79,0:00:15.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那·F·清英
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.35,0:00:21.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拯救我 引导我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.51,0:00:23.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而现在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.81,0:00:26.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又想在我面前以神自居吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.08,0:00:29.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我本来就是神
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.64,0:00:31.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么想支配人类吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.17,0:00:36.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不这样做 人类就会继续争斗直至灭亡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.23,0:00:39.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是救世主
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.98,0:00:43.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想共同奋斗吗 不想彼此理解吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.14,0:00:48.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和人类为一己私利管理动物一样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.53,0:00:56.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 若赢了你这个纯种 我的有用性就是不可动摇的了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.65,0:00:59.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这自私会扭曲世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.42,0:01:02.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你发动的再生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.12,0:01:04.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我来破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.48,0:01:06.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉悟不错
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.59,0:01:08.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,00-Raiser
