Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.71,0:01:13.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那·F·清英
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.01,0:01:15.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利冯兹·阿尔马克
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.04,0:01:16.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出击
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.85,0:01:17.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.90,0:03:00.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Veda发来通信
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.55,0:03:01.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Veda?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.82,0:03:06.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 说是脱离支援的新型机 正与00-Raiser交战中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.11,0:03:08.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说新型机?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.58,0:03:11.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出动托勒密
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.05,0:03:12.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾恩先生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.17,0:03:14.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.61,0:03:16.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.04,0:03:21.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掩护刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.35,0:03:21.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.85,0:03:25.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊安 准备炮击
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.93,0:03:26.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.54,0:03:31.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿勒路亚 能出动吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.60,0:03:33.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.93,0:03:38.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密发来通信 托勒密发来通信
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.03,0:03:42.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.72,0:03:46.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.90,0:03:56.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种程度的炮击
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.85,0:03:57.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能量充填还剩…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.18,0:04:11.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是 我的距离
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.19,0:04:19.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.34,0:04:35.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.09,0:04:38.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.10,0:04:48.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别以为Twin Drive系统是你独有的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.83,0:04:52.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是了 这架机体才是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.93,0:04:55.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引导人类的Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.65,0:05:05.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.69,0:05:38.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.78,0:05:42.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们来掩护 利冯兹·阿尔马克
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.85,0:05:45.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 多此一举
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.43,0:05:52.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算没有Veda的后援 区区人类
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.81,0:06:11.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.62,0:06:14.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂 阿勒路亚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.52,0:06:19.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超兵复活啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.27,0:06:22.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要战斗 我们的行动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.32,0:06:24.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事关未来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.41,0:06:33.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这小子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.27,0:06:43.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凭这种机体 就想对抗我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.01,0:06:53.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.86,0:07:00.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没了系统支持 变革者就这水平吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.09,0:07:25.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依赖Veda成了习惯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.43,0:07:28.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能赢我们才见鬼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.78,0:07:31.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救我 利冯兹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.56,0:07:37.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希林
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.96,0:07:54.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混…混账
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.75,0:08:07.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺有一手嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.38,0:08:14.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雕虫小技
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.48,0:08:21.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引擎部中弹 航行有碍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.13,0:08:23.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发射烟幕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.57,0:08:24.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 刹那也会
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.99,0:08:25.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发射
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.31,0:08:32.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干扰视线而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.11,0:08:34.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今的刹那能行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.25,0:08:52.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿下了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.11,0:09:05.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这力量
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.23,0:09:09.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是纯种的力量吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.47,0:09:20.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈罗 TRANS-AM呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.01,0:09:23.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可用1秒 可用1秒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.78,0:09:25.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.65,0:09:38.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,归我了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.59,0:10:04.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这才是…天人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.04,0:10:07.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾纽…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.69,0:10:12.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cherudim 击破敌机
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.89,0:10:14.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩余敌人只有Gundam型了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.52,0:10:18.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊安 听得见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.75,0:10:19.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.76,0:10:21.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备发射R2 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.93,0:10:23.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 预备Drive…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.87,0:10:24.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快准备
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.57,0:10:35.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这力量 全靠原版GN Drive的恩惠
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.88,0:10:39.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.85,0:10:41.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁听你的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.91,0:10:49.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 不这样被没有创造我的意义了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.69,0:10:51.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就没有我存在的意义了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.33,0:10:52.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.16,0:10:54.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提耶利亚·艾迪?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.97,0:10:55.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用Veda…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.00,0:10:58.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是为了引导人类
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.59,0:11:03.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是和人类共同创造未来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.46,0:11:10.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那才是我们原始变革体的正确道路
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.42,0:11:14.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和下等的人类一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.29,0:11:22.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因你总是如此藐视人类 才无法彼此理解
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.95,0:11:26.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可没这意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.02,0:11:31.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TRANS-AM
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.31,0:11:50.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休想
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.14,0:11:54.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然量子化了?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.94,0:12:03.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===============================
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.54,0:12:24.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于到手了 原版太阳炉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.18,0:12:28.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有它在手 我将成为伊欧利亚计划的实现者…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.30,0:12:32.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 甚至超越于那种存在之上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.20,0:12:36.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机体受损过重…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.84,0:12:37.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.26,0:12:49.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…命运啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.98,0:12:52.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还能再战!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.49,0:13:08.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.36,0:13:14.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs13\fsp70}　{\fsp1}Matching Clear{\r}\NGN Drive 匹配完成
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.11,0:13:15.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.98,0:13:18.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里 你在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.05,0:13:21.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那·F·清英
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.77,0:13:23.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.89,0:13:25.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有太阳炉?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.88,0:13:28.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难…难道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.49,0:13:30.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.37,0:13:37.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam Exia
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.35,0:13:42.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那·F·清英 开辟未来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.04,0:13:47.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这只蝼蚁之辈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.24,0:13:53.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.07,0:13:58.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便你最终无法读到这封信
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.00,0:14:04.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也请允许我将自己的思绪记述于此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.62,0:14:12.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为库尔吉斯的少年兵 被迫踏上战场
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.67,0:14:17.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能在战场上寻求生存之路的你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.67,0:14:23.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你我渴望和平的心情是何其相似
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.69,0:14:28.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此心有灵犀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.75,0:14:36.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们为何走上了不同的道路?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.43,0:14:46.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你欲图以武力消除世界上的纷争
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.53,0:14:51.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算付诸实现
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.07,0:14:56.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的幸福又在哪里?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.58,0:15:06.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背负罪孽 伤痕累累
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.92,0:15:10.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此 仍然坚持战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.90,0:15:17.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的生存方式 让人感觉如此悲壮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.77,0:15:25.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与他人分享自己心中的幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.37,0:15:30.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使它传播开来 才是成就真正的和平
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.21,0:15:32.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是这么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.74,0:15:37.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 希望你也能
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.08,0:15:40.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牢牢把握自己的幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.66,0:15:48.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那 祝幸福早日降临你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.02,0:15:58.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛莉娜殿下 时间到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.55,0:15:59.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.63,0:16:01.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.49,0:16:03.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.74,0:16:04.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.61,0:16:12.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我阿撒迪斯坦在地球联邦政府的援助下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.13,0:16:15.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于得以重建
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.44,0:16:23.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们将努力让这份援助扩大到中东各国
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.88,0:16:30.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽娜殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.64,0:16:34.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那 我要把这份小小的和平传播开来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.55,0:16:37.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如同故事 广为流传
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.44,0:16:41.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如歌声渗人心扉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.35,0:16:52.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,侵蚀路易丝身体的细胞异常反应
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.55,0:16:55.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经完全停止恶化
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.86,0:17:00.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是靠刹那发出的那道光芒所赐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.12,0:17:05.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法得知真相与缘由也罢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.42,0:17:10.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少 她就在我身边
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.15,0:17:12.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.69,0:17:16.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是新的联邦总统
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.50,0:17:24.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,KATARON的成员亦在其中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.26,0:17:28.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屡次屠杀民众
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.50,0:17:33.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妄图操纵情报掩盖真相的独立治安维持部队将解体
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.23,0:17:37.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球联邦军重编在即
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.02,0:17:43.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续加大对非联邦成员国家的援助 并推进其早日加入联邦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.12,0:17:49.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在此宣布 将尽一切努力树立新地球联邦政府
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.15,0:17:59.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界从这一刻开始改变
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.81,0:18:02.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 但只是开始
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.43,0:18:06.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手牵手建设互相理解的和平世界
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.36,0:18:09.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话虽简单
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.72,0:18:12.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我们任重道远
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.27,0:18:15.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也为即将诞生的孩子们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.70,0:18:17.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是啊 克劳斯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.54,0:18:20.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们必须从自身开始改变
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.47,0:18:22.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.16,0:18:26.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为树立真正意义上的地球联邦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.78,0:18:29.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们必须从新的三项…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.72,0:18:30.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 沙慈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.72,0:18:34.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界将迎来怎样的变化呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.11,0:18:38.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说实话 我也不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.14,0:18:43.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但人们不能继续懵然不觉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.28,0:18:46.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出生在和平中的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.09,0:18:51.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解了现实 了解了战争
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.05,0:18:53.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意识到它的宝贵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.17,0:19:01.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有必要反思 真心盼望和平的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.07,0:19:04.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人人都必须对这个世界进行反思
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.25,0:19:06.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.41,0:19:14.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准将 司令部对天人的处置有何说法?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.68,0:19:17.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们也是铲除腐败组织A-LAWS的有功之人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.35,0:19:23.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但只要不放弃武力 对于现政权
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.78,0:19:24.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仍旧是危险的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.13,0:19:28.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们如有动静 我们立即行动
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.87,0:19:29.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.77,0:19:31.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.61,0:19:33.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.87,0:19:35.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进来前先敲门!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.36,0:19:37.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我已经升为准将了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.52,0:19:39.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.01,0:19:42.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 时间已经过了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.00,0:19:45.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女主角怎么能姗姗来迟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.45,0:19:46.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.64,0:19:55.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不死之身的戈拉索瓦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.05,0:19:58.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今变成幸福的戈拉索瓦了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.89,0:20:02.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你没辙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.55,0:20:15.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我选择作为军人活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.11,0:20:19.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保护市民 与威胁和平的势力做斗争
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.26,0:20:23.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在父亲与母亲奉献毕生的岗位上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.82,0:20:34.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲 母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.87,0:20:37.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾米 哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.29,0:20:44.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我脱离KATARON 作为Gundam Meister活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.19,0:20:49.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为洛克昂·史特拉特斯 面对这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.28,0:20:53.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算被世人所不齿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.05,0:20:57.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会战斗至天罚降临
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.38,0:21:01.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还须时日才能与你们重逢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.53,0:21:06.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会等我到那一天吧 艾纽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.26,0:21:12.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界又面临着翻天覆地的变化
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.45,0:21:17.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此 我们犯下的滔天罪行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.25,0:21:21.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夺走人生命的罪行 绝不会…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.17,0:21:24.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿勒路亚…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.25,0:21:31.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个世界充满矛盾 我自身也是矛盾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.58,0:21:35.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 必须去改变
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.47,0:21:41.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寻找我们生存的意义…其答案
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.99,0:21:50.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此一来 未来就取决于人类了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.90,0:21:53.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我作为Veda的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.60,0:21:56.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,选择在一旁守护你们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.04,0:22:00.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直至即将到来的对话成为现实
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.42,0:22:03.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了 大家
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.15,0:22:11.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界今后会如何 没有人知道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.33,0:22:16.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 我想它会向好的方向发展
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.40,0:22:20.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过去是无法被改变的 但未来仍在人们手中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.39,0:22:24.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,创造我们心中祈盼的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.12,0:22:27.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我们错了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.81,0:22:32.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦事与愿违 战火再起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.26,0:22:36.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们肯定会再次挺身而出
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.94,0:22:41.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,义无反顾地将所有矛盾揽入怀中…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.65,0:22:47.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出发吧 我们的工作远未结束
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.62,0:22:53.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 必须守护大家用生命换来的新世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.84,0:22:54.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.11,0:23:02.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是天人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.87,0:23:04.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以根绝战争为目标之人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.38,0:23:08.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便被世界抛弃
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.94,0:23:12.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也必须认真面对这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.37,0:23:17.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不惜行使武力 作为一股威慑力量活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.63,0:23:25.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们 必须继续存在于世
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.48,0:23:27.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了未来…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.22,0:23:56.12,yugao,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)}人类的童年结束
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.12,0:24:01.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剧场版 机动战士高达00 2010年公开
